  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Reorganizing Risk Key Figures in Evaluation Currency</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loio3dfbc5536a51204be10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Reorganizing Risk Key Figures in Evaluation Currency </h1><div class=\"body\">\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Use\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"> See <a class=\"xref\" href=\"69fac5536a51204be10000000a174cb4.html\">Performance Functions for Reporting</a>\n</p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Procedure\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Procedure</h2>\n<ol class=\"ol\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Start the function [transaction TRMP_PERFORMANCE_MVT] ( <span class=\"ph\">path</span> ). The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Change View \"Reporting: Buffer Table for Market Values – Evaluation Currency\"</span> screen appears.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Select the data you want to delete. The following utilities are available to help you:\n</p><ol class=\"ol\" type=\"a\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">You can restrict the data volume by choosing <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Selection</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">By Contents</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span> .The possible selection criteria include:\n</p><ul class=\"ul\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Evaluation type in Risk Management\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Evaluation currency\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Net present value in evaluation currency\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Net present value outgoing side in evaluation currency\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Net present value incoming side in evaluation currency\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Basis point value in evaluation currency\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Company Code\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Valuation Area\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Clean price in evaluation currency\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Securities account\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Financial transaction\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Security ID number\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Futures account\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Key Date\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Contract number\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Changed by\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Changed on\n</p></li></ul></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">You can select all data or a certain block of data by choosing <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Edit</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Selections</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span> .\n</p></li></ol></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Edit</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Delete</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span> to remove the selected lines from the table.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Save your changes.\n</p></li></ol>\n</section></div>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
